quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,"Kandi mbere yabo (ababangikanyamana) twagerageje abantu ba Farawo, ubwo intumwa yubahitse (Musa) yabageragaho"
  44,18,"(Irababwira iti) \"Nimumpe abagaragu ba Allah (mbajyane). Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi intumwa yizewe iboherejwemo"
  44,19,Ntimukanishyire hejuru imbere ya Allah. Rwose mbazaniye ibimenyetso bigaragara
  44,20,"Kandi nikinze kuri Nyagasani wanjye ari na we Nyagasani wanyu, kugira ngo mutantera amabuye"
  44,21,Ariko nimutananyemera mundeke (ntimungirire nabi)
  44,22,"(Nuko bashaka kumugirira nabi) maze atakambira Nyagasani we agira ati \"Mu by’ukuri, aba bantu ni abagizi ba nabi (ubandinde)"
  44,23,"(Allah aramubwira ati) \"Ujyane n’abagaragu banjye nijoro; rwose (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kubakurikira"
  44,24,"(Nimumara kwambuka) ureke inyanja igume uko iri ituje. Mu by’ukuri, (Farawo n’ingabo ze) baraza kurohama"
  44,25,(Ese Farawo n’abantu be) basize ubusitani n’imigezi bingana iki
  44,26,Ibihingwa n’amazu meza
  44,27,Naho umudendezo babagamo banezerewe
  44,28,Uko ni ko byagenze! (Imitungo yabo) twayizunguje abandi bantu
  44,29,Ikirere n’isi ntibyigeze bibaririra123 kandi ntibigeze bakererezwa (guhanwa)
  44,30,Kandi rwose twarokoye bene Isiraheli ibihano bisuzuguza
  44,31,"Bya Farawo, wari warishyize hejuru akaba n’umwangizi"
  44,32,(Bene Isiraheli) twabatoranyije tubizi tubarutisha ibiremwa (byo ku gihe cyabo)
  44,33,Twanabahaye ibitangaza birimo ibigeragezo bigaragara
  44,34,"Mu by’ukuri, abo (bahakanyi b’i Maka) baravuga bati"
  44,35,"Rwose nta rundi rupfu ruzabaho usibye urupfu rwacu rwa mbere (abantu bose bapfa), ndetse nta n’ubwo tuzazurwa"
  44,36,Ngaho nimugarure abakurambere bacu (bapfuye kera) niba muvuga ukuri (ko Allah azazura abapfuye)
  44,37,"Ese abo (babangikanyamana) nibo beza cyangwa se abantu ba Tubba’i124, ndetse na babandi babayeho mbere yabo? (Abo bose) twaraboretse kubera ko bari abagizi ba nabi"
  44,38,Ntabwo twaremye ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo dukina
  44,39,Nta kindi cyatumye tubirema uretse ku mpamvu z’ukuri; nyamara abenshi muri bo ntibabizi
  44,40,"Mu by’ukuri, umunsi w’urubanza (ubwo Allah azakiranura ibiremwa), ni wo munsi w’isezerano rya bose"
  44,41,"Umunsi inshuti magara itazagira icyo imarira inshuti magara ngenzi yayo, ndetse nta n’ubwo bazatabarwa"
  44,42,"Uretse uwo Allah azagirira impuhwe. Mu by’ukuri, (Allah) ni Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  44,43,"Mu by’ukuri, igiti cya Zaqumu"
  44,44,Kizaba amafunguro y’abanyabyaha
  44,45,"(Ayo mafunguro azaba ameze) nk’umuringa washongeshejwe, uzaba utogotera mu nda"
  44,46,Nko gutogota kw’amazi yatuye
  44,47,"(Hazatangwa itegeko rigira riti) \"Nimumufate mumukururire rwagati mu muriro uguramana"
  44,48,Maze mumusuke mu mutwe amazi yatuye nk’igihano
  44,49,"(Maze abwirwe ati) \"Sogongera! Mu by’ukuri, (wajyaga wibwira ko) uri umunyembaraga ukaba n’umunyacyubahiro"
  44,50,"Mu by’ukuri, iki ni cyo (gihano) mwajyaga mushidikanyaho"
  44,51,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari ahantu hatekanye (mu Ijuru)"
  44,52,Mu busitani n’imigezi
  44,53,"Bazaba bambaye imyambaro ikoze mu ihariri yorohereye ndetse n’iremereye, barebana"
  44,54,"Uko ni ko bizaba bimeze. Tuzanabashyingira Huur ul-a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro, b’amaso manini)"
  44,55,"Bazarihererwamo imbuto (z’ubwoko bwose), batekanye"
  44,56,"Ntabwo bazasogongeramo urupfu uretse urupfu rwa mbere (bari ku isi), kandi Allah azabarinda ibihano by’umuriro ugurumana"
  44,57,Bizaba ari ingabire ziturutse kwa Nyagasani wawe! Iyo ni yo izaba ari intsinzi ihambaye
  44,58,"Mu by’ukuri, (Qur’an) twarayoroheje mu rurimi rwawe (rw’Icyarabu), kugira ngo bibuke (maze bibabere isomo)"
  44,59,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) tegereza (ibyo nagusezeranyije bizababaho), mu by’ukuri nabo bategereje (ibizakubaho)"
  45,1,Haa Miim
  45,2,"Ihishurwa ry’iki gitabo (Qur’an) rituruka kwa Allah, Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushishoza"
  45,3,"Mu by’ukuri, (ukuremwa) kw’ibirere n’isi ni ibimenyetso ku bemeramana"
  45,4,"No mu iremwa ryanyu ndetse n’uburyo (Allah) akwirakwiza inyamaswa (ku isi), ni ibimenyetso ku bantu bemera badashidikanya"
  45,5,"No mu gusimburana kw’ijoro n’amanywa ndetse n’amafunguro (imvura) Allah amanura mu kirere, akayahesha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa kwayo (gukakara), ndetse n’ihindagurika ry’imiyaga; ni ibimenyetso ku bantu bafite ubwenge"
  45,6,Ayo ni amagambo ya Allah tugusomera mu kuri (yewe Muhamadi). Ese ni ayahe magambo yandi bakemera nyuma y’amagambo ya Allah ndetse n’ibimenyetso bye
  45,7,"Ibihano bikaze bizaba kuri buri wese uhimba ibinyoma, w’umunyabyaha"
  45,8,"Wawundi usomerwa amagambo ya Allah, maze agatsimbarara, agatera umugongo yibona nk’aho atayumvise. (Yewe Muhamadi) muhe inkuru y’ibihano bibabaza"
  45,9,N’iyo hari icyo amenye mu magambo yacu arayacyerensa. Abo bazahanishwa ibihano bisuzuguza
  45,10,"Kandi n’imbere yabo hari umuriro wa Jahanamu, kandi ibyo bakoze cyangwa izindi mana bishyiriyeho zitari Allah ntacyo bizabamarira. Ndetse bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"
  45,11,(Iyi Qur’an) ni wo muyoboro. Naho babandi bahakanye amagambo ya Nyagasani wabo bazahanishwa ibihano bibi cyane kandi bibabaza